CSS Cheatsheet
==============
/* comments looks like this */

CSS Box model:
 -----------------------
|		Margin			|
|  +++++Border++++++++  |
|  +	Padding		 +	|
|  +   -----------   +	|
|  +  | Content   |  +	|
|  +   -----------	 +  |
|  +++++++++++++++++++	|
 -----------------------
Content - the content of the box
Padding - area around the content
Border - around the padding and content
Margin - an area outside the border

Selectors
---------
* {}									Refer to all html body
#id {}									Create id in html: <h1 id="idName">
.class {}								Create class in html: <div class="className">
h1.class								Only headers in class. Can be paragraphs as well
h1 {}, h2 {}, h3 {}, h1 + p {}
h1 ~ p {}
ul > li {}

Box Properties
--------------
p.ex1 {
	height: auto | 10px | 23% | 
	width: 300px;
 	border: 15px solid green;
 	padding: 50px;
 	margin: 20px;
	box-sizing: border-box | content-box
	margin: 2px 4px 6px 8px | 0 auto
	margin-bottom: 100px;				Can be: margin-right, margin-left, margin-top
	padding: 2px 4px 6px 8px			top,right,bottom,left
	border: 1px solid black;
	border-color: #2AA9E0
	border-style: none | hidden | dotted | dashed | solid | double | groove | ridge | inset | outset
	border-width: 10px
	outline: 1px solid red;
 	outline-offset: 15px;
	outline-style: solid;
 	outline-color: red;
 	outline-width: thick;
}

Position
--------
* {
	position: static | relative | absolute | fixed | sticky
	postion: top | right | bottom | left
	clear: none | left | right | both
	float: left | right | none
	z-index: 3 | auto | inherit
}

Backgroud
---------
.bakcground {
	background-image: url()
	background-color: #2AA9E0
	background-position: top | right | bottom | left | center
	background-repeat: repeat-x | repeat-y | repeat | space | round | no-repeat
	background-attachment: scroll | fixed | local | initial | inherit
}

Text Styling
------------
div {
	font-style: normal | italic | oblique
	font-variant: normal | small-caps
	font-weight: normal | bold | bolder | lighter | 100 - 900
	vertical-align: baseline | 10px | sub | super | top | text-top | middle | bottom | text-bottom | initial
	text-transform: capitalise | lowercase | uppercase
	font-size: 12px | 0.8em | 80%
	letter-spacing: normal | 4px
	line-height: normal | 3em | 34%
	text-align: left | right | center | justify
	text-align-last: auto | left | right | center | justify | start | end | initial | inherit
	text-decoration: none | underline | overline | line-through
	text-indent: 25px
	font-family: 'Open Sans', sans
	text-justify: auto | inter-word | inter-character | none | initial | inherit
	text-overflow: clip | ellipsis | string | initial | inherit
	text-shadow: h-shadow v-shadow blur-radius color | none | initial | inherit
}



